<h3 style="margin-bottom: 18px !important; vertical-align: middle; text-align: left;"><span style="color: #936502; font-family: 'Alice', serif; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Milana</span></h3>
<p class="p1">RESPONSABLE DES LICENCES</p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone " style="margin-right: 12px;" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%2017%2017'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="phone1" width="17" height="17" title="Règlement MICA 13" data-lazy-src="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/phone1.svg"><noscript><img decoding="async" class="alignnone " style="margin-right: 12px;" src="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/phone1.svg" alt="phone1" width="17" height="17" title="Règlement MICA 13"></noscript>+370 661 75988<br />
<img decoding="async" class="alignnone " style="margin-right: 12px; margin-top: -6px;" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%2019%2019'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="email2" width="19" height="19" title="Règlement MICA 14" data-lazy-src="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/email2.svg"><noscript><img decoding="async" class="alignnone " style="margin-right: 12px; margin-top: -6px;" src="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/email2.svg" alt="email2" width="19" height="19" title="Règlement MICA 14"></noscript><strong><a href="mailto: milana.s@regulatedunitedeurope.com">milana.s@regulatedunitedeurope.com</a></strong></p>
<div class="vc_btn3-container btn vc_btn3-center vc_custom_1651818670905" style="text-align: center;"><a class="vc_general vc_btn3 vc_btn3-size-md vc_btn3-shape-rounded vc_btn3-style-custom" style="background-color: #f5a700; color: #000000;" title="" href="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/fr/contact-us/">Contactez-moi</a></div>
